<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">周颂·振鹭</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contsona9ccb1a3e8be">
<p>振鹭于飞，于彼西雍。我客戾止，亦有斯容。在彼无恶，在此无斁。庶几夙夜，以永终誉。</p>
</div>
</div>
